# Career Connections Overview

#### The <a href="https://code.org/en-US/curriculum/artificial-intelligence-foundations" target="blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AI Foundations Curriculum</a> integrates career exploration and emerging technologies as students develop foundational skills in computing.

#### Throughout the course, students engage with real-world case studies, hands-on projects, and industry-relevant tools to see how cybersecurity skills apply across various fields. 

<h2 style="text-align: center;">Emerging Technologies</h2>

